## JavaScript dengan HTML Element

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <title>Hello World JavaScript</title>
    <style>
       body {
           Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
           margin-top: 50px;
        }
       #output {
           font-size: 24px;
            blue;
          margin: 20px;
        }
        button {
           padding: 10px 20px;
           font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
   </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>JavaScript Hello World</h1>
    <div id="output">Klik tombol untuk Hello World!</div>
    <button onclick="showHello()">Klik Saya</button>

    <script>
        function showHello() {
           document.getElementById('output').innerHTML = "Hello World!";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

## 3. Standalone JavaScript (File .js)

```javascript
// hello.js
console.log("Hello World!");

// Dengan function
function sayHello() {
    console.log("Hello World!");
    World!");
    return "Hello World!";
}

// Panggil function
sayHello();
```

## Modern JavaScript (ES6+)

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <title>Modern Hello World</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Modern JavaScript Hello World</h1>
   <div id="app"></div>

    <script type="module">
        // Arrow function
        const helloWorld = () => {
           console.log("Hello World!");
           document.getElementById('app').innerHTML = "Hello World!";
        };
              // Auto execute
        helloWorld();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

## Cara Menjalankan:

1. **Browser**: Simpan sebagai file `.html` lalu buka di browser
2. **Node.js**: Simpan sebagai `hello.js` lalu jalankan `node hello.js`
3. **Console**: Bisa langsung di Developer Tools browser

